reviewText: This Is Blondes Having Too Much Fun!!!!!!!!!!

Box art not on product, featueres 7 scenes, a gal with big lips wearing wings in front of a motorcycle, shaved; a gal on a couch pierced navel, a cowgirl, trimmed; on the beach girl-girl; two different gals in Little Black Dresses, pierced navel. Music, disrobe. Not too memerable, can be watch again.
I either never received this or threw it away immediately, because I do not recall ever seeing it.  But since you want me to rate, there's my rating.

I  like this DVD because it shows just about everthing in details and plus I thought the camera shots of each girl was done very well. I also paid a reasonable price for it and I thought it was well worth it. I highly recommend this DVD to
anyone. Rated By Buyer Ricky R.
